the news about your gig.

34:26.708 --> 34:30.001
It's so great
I just had to tell everyone.

34:30.126 --> 34:32.208
That's okay.
- Good.

34:32.458 --> 34:36.376
It's great you're going all the way
to Norway to play a gig.

34:36.501 --> 34:41.542
