to get one around here.

34:48.333 --> 34:50.333
Jouni.

34:51.542 --> 34:54.542
Miia. Should we finally check
the backstage out?

34:54.667 --> 34:57.792
Why don't you take the boys
as your opening act.

35:00.292 --> 35:05.001
Right. Well...
I wonder how that would work out.

35:05.126 --> 35:07.542
Give the boys a chance.

35:08.917 --> 35:13.376
Well, it would be a nice change
to have a comedy act here.

35:14.501 --> 35:17.792
So what do you say, Moilanen?
You wanna open -

35:17.917 --> 35:20.417
for the Star Mustaches
next Saturday?

35:20.792 --> 35:23.126
Say yes!

35:24.001 --> 35:27.334
Sure.
- Yes!

35:27.542 --> 35:31.459
That's awesome! Thanks, Jouni,
that's so nice of you!

35:31.584 --> 35:35.084
My pleasure.
- Yes!

35:39.209 --> 35:42.209
What kind of music
do you retards even play?

35:42.501 --> 35:45.542
Symphonic post-apocalyptic
reindeer-grinding -

35:45.667 --> 35:49.084
Christ-abusing extreme
war pagan Fennoscandian metal.

35:51.126 --> 35:53.417
No wonder
you're not getting any pussy.

35:53.542 --> 35:57.584
And who stuck a pole up his ass?
One of you?

35:58.251 --> 36:00.251
Frigging ghost.

36:04.334 --> 36:07.167
Impaled Ass...

36:15.751 --> 36:18.334
We want the best van
we can get for this money.

36:19.251 --> 36:24.001
That's 260.
- Yeah. What can we get with it?

36:24.084 --> 36:28.751
A snow tire and gonorrhea.
Barely.

36:31.126 --> 36:35.209
Okay, I'll trade my Peugeot 205
for the van.

36:35.334 --> 36:37.167
XL?
- Yeah.

36:38.876 --> 36:44.292
285 euros.
I might have a van for you.

36:52.751 --> 36:56.209
This is it.
It has a beautiful patina.

36:56.626 --> 36:59.209
It's seen a lot of life.
Or actually death.

36:59.376 --> 37:02.584
This van has killed
three large animals and one person.

37:02.709 --> 37:05.667
A dwarf. Chinese, I think.

37:06.001 --> 37:10.001
Then it was buried in a swamp.

37:10.167 --> 37:14.209
It was used
in a bank robbery in Sweden.

37:14.501 --> 37:16.876
And a circus professional,
a clown, -

37:17.001 --> 37:19.584
killed himself
in the passenger seat.

37:23.501 --> 37:25.501
It's the van of death.

37:26.251 --> 37:28.084
<i>The death van.</i>

37:29.459 --> 37:32.417
Yes. We'll take it.

37:35.709 --> 37:37.667
Okay.

37:42.417 --> 37:45.501
Jynkky, why don't you lend me
your old drums.

37:45.626 --> 37:48.084
We'll take them
to the care home. - Why?

37:48.209 --> 37:49.834
For music therapy.

37:50.001 --> 37:54.667
Fuck! It clicked again.
That damn speed camera haunts me!

37:54.792 --> 37:56.667
We could've taken another road.

37:56.792 --> 37:59.126
I've been taking this road -

37:59.251 --> 38:01.542
since before
I got my driver's license.

38:01.667 --> 38:04.334
I ain't taking back roads
because of that cam.

38:04.459 --> 38:06.251
That cost me 100 euros.

38:12.584 --> 38:17.126
Sweet Jesus on a stick!
I never would've believed it.

38:18.001 --> 38:21.251
Take new linens to him.
And then there's Kolehmainen...

38:23.001 --> 38:26.876
I heard you have a gig at the hotel.
- Yeah.

38:27.084 --> 38:30.876
A bunch of the staff
will be there.

39:03.001 --> 39:04.917
This is a great song!

39:07.667 --> 39:09.626
What is it?

39:09.834 --> 39:13.292
My buddies and I have a band.
- Are you famous?

39:14.001 --> 39:16.001
I don't know about that.

39:16.626 --> 39:20.876
